==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One thing beats another.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī wù kè yī wù

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[物]][[克]][[一]][[物]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# There is always one thing to conquer another.
# Everything has its vanquisher.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[物]][[剋]][[一]][[物]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

